# Coding Rules
#
# Git attributes can enforce line endings. UTF-8 BOM policy is documented in
# docs/CodingRules.md and must be checked by tools/review because Git attributes
# cannot portably require UTF-8 with BOM across environments.

* text=auto eol=crlf

# Codex skill loader requires SKILL.md frontmatter to start at byte 0, so these
# files must be UTF-8 without BOM while still using CRLF line endings.
.codex/skills/**/SKILL.md text eol=crlf
